{"id": 1987, "genre": 1001, "title": "成长的过程中，你已经原谅了自己哪些弱点？", "description": "不跟自己较劲，是我保持心智成熟情绪稳定最重要的心得。", "record_count": 3364, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171101180722jgiBEuplTrP6RQ09.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-11-02T03:00:38Z", "options": [{"id": 245760, "content": "情商低", "image": null, "praise_count": 28, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173723}, {"id": 246016, "content": "矮....总是控制不住想爆发的小情绪...用运动音乐较劲一年...更好的看清自己...继续向前", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174192}, {"id": 246272, "content": "自慰", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1174777}, {"id": 249600, "content": "胖 懒 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163441}, {"id": 245761, "content": "内向", "image": null, "praise_count": 54, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 133780}, {"id": 246017, "content": "自私", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1102095}, {"id": 248833, "content": "怂", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1184185}, {"id": 245762, "content": "原谅一切自己犯的错误", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1173724}, {"id": 246018, "content": "总是对自己在乎的人或事，说错话。自私", "image": null, "praise_count": 8, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1066369}, {"id": 246274, "content": "没脑子", "image": "img/option/option/20171103144701WwcdulYKFH9qT2V4.jpg", "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1042654}, {"id": 247810, "content": "太过理性", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1110856}, {"id": 264707, "content": "允许自己将就，允许自己委屈。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 853433}, {"id": 246019, "content": "不想受束缚", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1165093}, {"id": 245764, "content": "原谅自己的不完美！小缺点，毕竟不是圣人～", "